      "writtenOn": "2019-08-15T12:24:33Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I\u0027m not quite sure what this means. Empty branch?  If possible, could we use a constant like GARBAGE_COLLECT_BRANCH or DELETE_BRANCH instead of a raw empty string? Would make it a bit more readable.",
